A static web server
Has a configuration file which should be named as staticserver.conf
For configuration the system should be:

staticserver.<id>.virtualhost
staticserver.<id>.documentroot
staticserver.<id>.wellcome

id is an integer starting from 0. it should be continues.
virtualhost is the domain like www.example.com
documentroot is the folder of files reside.
wellcome is the enterance page

The jar should be deployed at osgi container bundle dir. It requires nanohttpd
bundle.

The maven repository is:

<repository>
        <id>sanaldiyar-snapshot</id>
        <name>Sanal Diyar Snapshot</name>
        <url>http://maven2.sanaldiyar.com/snap-repo/</url>
</repository>

